      <source xsi:type="org.nasdanika.exec.content:Text" uuid="5231daea-600f-4acc-bdf8-4df15cad6cb5" content="*&#xA;Functional (Logical) User Interface Metamodel&#xA;&#xA;A renderer-agnostic model representing the logical intent and data requirements of a UI.&#xA;The downstream rendering engine decides how each element is physically rendered&#xA;(e.g., HTML, Bootstrap, React)."/>
    </source>
  </content>
